    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Replace this with a proper description.</em>\n<details>\n<summary>Credits and Instructions</summary>\n<h2>Made by Elwin</h2>\nBased on Christopher version.\n <h3>Requires:</h3>\n<ul>\n   <li>Times-up</li>\n   <li>Elwin Helpers (Enable in Settings)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Usage:</strong></p>\n<p>This item is used as a factory to create Oathbow bows. Open this item and select its effects tab.\nOpen the bow to be transformed into an Oathbow, then drag drop the 'Oathbow' enchantment effect on the target weapon.\nThe enchantment adds an activity to swear an oath when equipped and attuned.\nWhen this activity is used, it allows to swear an oath to designate a sworn enemy, this applies one AE on the attacker \nand one on the target to be able to apply the effects. When a sworn enemy is attacked with this bow, it applies its effects.</p></details>",
